'''2019年环西自行车赛'''是第74届[[环西自行车赛|环西自行车赛]]，于2019年8月24日至9月15日进行，此次比赛是2019年UCI世界巡回赛的其中一站比赛<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cyclingnews.com/news/uci-reveal-worldtour-calendar-for-2019/|title=UCI reveal WorldTour calendar for 2019|work=Cycling News|date=2018-06-15|accessdate=2018-08-27|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200929135630/https://www.cyclingnews.com/news/uci-reveal-worldtour-calendar-for-2019/|archivedate=2020-09-29}}{{cbignore}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://movistarteam.com/en/2019-08-19/2019-vuelta-espana-lineup|title=Movistar Team announces Vuelta a España lineup|work=Movistar Team|date=2019-08-19|accessdate=2020-09-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191116125657/https://movistarteam.com/en/2019-08-19/2019-vuelta-espana-lineup|archivedate=2019-11-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。比赛共分为21个赛段，起点位于[[托雷维耶哈|托雷维耶哈]]，终点位于[[马德里|马德里]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ciclo21.com/vuelta-espana-2019/|title=Vuelta España 2019: Las Salinas de Torrevieja darán la salida|work=Ciclo21|first=Nicolás|last=Van Looy|date=2018-08-25|accessdate=2018-08-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180829102435/http://www.ciclo21.com/vuelta-espana-2019/|archivedate=2018-08-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

共有22支车队参加此次比赛，其中18支车队为世界职业车队，另外4支车队则为洲际职业车队<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cyclingnews.com/news/vuelta-a-espana-announces-four-wildcard-teams/|title=Vuelta a Espana announces four wildcard teams|work=Cycling News|date=2019-05-07|accessdate=2020-09-29|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200929140611/https://www.cyclingnews.com/news/vuelta-a-espana-announces-four-wildcard-teams/|archivedate=2020-09-29}}{{cbignore}}</ref>。最终来自Jumbo–Visma车队的[[普里莫日·羅格里奇|普里莫日·羅格里奇]]赢得此次比赛的总冠军，成为历史上首位在三大自行车赛上获得总冠军的斯洛文尼亚人<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.uci.org/road/news/2019/la-vuelta-a-espana-primo%C5%BE-rogli%C4%8D-becomes-the-first-ever-slovenian-grand-tour-winner|title=La Vuelta a España: Primož Roglič becomes the first ever Slovenian Grand Tour winner!|work=UCI|date=2019-09-16|accessdate=2020-09-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191102185648/https://www.uci.org/road/news/2019/la-vuelta-a-espana-primo%C5%BE-rogli%C4%8D-becomes-the-first-ever-slovenian-grand-tour-winner|archivedate=2019-11-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。移动之星车队选手[[Alejandro_Valverde|Alejandro Valverde]]获得第二名，Roglič的同胞，来自阿联酋航空车队的[[塔德伊·波加薩爾|塔德伊·波加薩爾]]则获得第三名<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.eurosport.com/cycling/vuelta-a-espana/2019/la-vuelta-a-espana-2019-news-primoz-roglic-triumphs-for-first-grand-tour-crown-in-madrid_sto7461694/story.shtml|title=Primoz Roglic celebrates first Grand Tour triumph in Madrid|publisher=Eurosport|date=2019-09-16|accessdate=2020-09-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190916062406/https://www.eurosport.com/cycling/vuelta-a-espana/2019/la-vuelta-a-espana-2019-news-primoz-roglic-triumphs-for-first-grand-tour-crown-in-madrid_sto7461694/story.shtml|archivedate=2019-09-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

